descriptionHtml:
Osare Panty for CHSBHC, originally by anano: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/users/3496215
[contains all colors and scripts from original as this mod only changes the .nif\'s :D ]

[b]Requirements[/b]: 

-original mod here: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/26305.
-one of these 2 files: [b]full CHSBHC[/b] or [b]weight slider[/b] support.

[b]Installation[/b]: 
fire up main mod, overwrite with this one. Hopefully NMM compatible :D

[b]Known Issues[/b]: 

-some clipping when walking between legs, at hips
-some clipping when sneaking between legs
-PM me if there are any texture issues, I tried to stay within original
  mod bounds.
author: anano
